# Generated theme file – regenerated at runtime by theme-sync.ts (writeThemeTokenColors).
# NOTE: the file shipped in the package is declared in package.json contributes.themes
# and must be packaged, so we do NOT ignore it here. (The runtime profile override of the
# same filename lives under ~/.ftr10 and is covered by the repo-root .gitignore.)

